The paper deals with a MIMO precoding scheme for wireless communication in OFDM systems, which involves signal processing and optimization techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory), which deals with the mathematical foundations of communication systems. The paper also involves wireless communication, which falls under cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The use of concentration of measure is a statistical technique, which could place the paper under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) or cs.COM (Computers and Society). Finally, the paper involves multiuser MIMO, which could place it under cs.MM (Multimedia).
